cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SI

This paper deals with the control of unknown nonlinear systems using Gaussian Process techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also uses machine learning techniques such as Gaussian Process, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper deals with optimization problems, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with uncertainty propagation, which could place it in cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
